Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.30,0:00:04.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The light of summer is the radiance of yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.16,0:00:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the tears is the ramen shop owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thought to exist, but actually doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth behind the police officer that vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.83,0:00:13.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:59.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This happened on the first Sunday of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:01.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, he's slow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:04.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:05.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here! Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here! Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:09.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The news that you've been dying to tell us...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:18.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you guys watch the Saturday drama yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean "Run! The Running of 100 Police Officers," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.53,0:02:25.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We watched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I noticed this right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:33.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That drama must have been filmed in this Beika Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously, who doesn't already know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi already knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:41.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The case happened in this park."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The main character shouted that cliche like it had\Nbeen said somewhere before over there, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The flowers in the background hadn't blossomed yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indicating that the filming was likely done at least half a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me this was the big news you had for us, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.36,0:03:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:06.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I was the only one who noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that drama wasn't very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:16.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only the part with the groups of uniformed\Nofficers running was actually funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you guys stop talking about the drama?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:29.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:31.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Akimoto Yasuyo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:35.23,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Akimoto Yasuyo (24)\N{\fs14} Office Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:34.33,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,She lives on 3rd Street now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:36.86,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,She used to live in the apartment next to where I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you go shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:42.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a snack sent from my hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was going to give it to a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A police officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though I don't know his name...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a very hard-working person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He even had a beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:06.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A beard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanna see him too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:12.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no one like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one has a beard and wears glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No—not here, and no one like that at\Nthe Beika Police Headquarters either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I saw him many times while he was patrolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there really isn't someone like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:35.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I instantly recalled that uniformed police officers\Naren't allowed to have noticeable facial hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:45.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, that person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't just call me whenever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we have something to tell you, Detective Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't a fake police officer an issue for police officers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:08.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fake police officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone who isn't a police officer and yet disguises as one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:19.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To fake his identity in that way is definitely an unforgivable crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:23.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you saw that person many times, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:24.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of work, I had to stay late every night last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:32.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was home late every night, up to last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first time I saw that police officer\Nwas the very first night I stayed late...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Monday night...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was walking towards 3rd Street,\Nwhere I live, after getting off the last train...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really dangerous for a young girl to be walking by herself at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please be extremely careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, I saw him every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, I saw that police officer every night that week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Several days earlier, I saw him helping an elderly couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't go out late at night, it's really dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife suddenly just had to have some cider.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:14.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you wanted to have some pudding?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:22.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night, he was helping a drunk man get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:24.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, pull yourself together...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is your house still far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:28.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:30.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll call a taxi for you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine aaalll by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You won't be fine at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll help you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're always having some kind of trouble, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please have a safe journey home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:47.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He seems like a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it's natural to believe he was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:56.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why did that person disguise as a police officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:06:59.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His intention...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Disguising as a policeman, he's likely aiming to do bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bad things, like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure about that part yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hi, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a theft several days ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we haven't found the culprit yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From his methods, it seems like all the thefts from\Nthis past week were done by the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:28.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were more thefts?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:32.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't there somebody else that's seen that person before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:35.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such as that old couple and that drunken man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we go ask them, we can probably find some clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:41.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, do you know who they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:45.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't recognize that drunken man, but the senior couple...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've seen them many times at Tetsuryuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:50.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tetsuryuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:55.07,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Odawara Tetsuji (33)\N{\fs13} Ramen Shop Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.07,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Fake police officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He seems angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More like very angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not angry at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:05.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although this owner seems unsociable, his ramen is very delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I often eat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:11.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:13.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:18.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is the secret of the ramen shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't just touch anything you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It flew on my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I sent it flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:33.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though I haven't eaten yet, I smell like ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:35.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:43.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, we came here to gather more\Ninformation on that fake police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:48.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an old couple who seems to get along really\Nwell with each other that seem to come here a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takayanagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think they live...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that old couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fake police officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:02.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys must have made a mistake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man is very nice and gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has a good reputation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:14.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're getting nowhere at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is he really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone just called in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:25.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a theft on 2nd Street last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:29.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, didn't you say\Nsomething about serial burglaries earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:30.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I've figure out the identity of the fake police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:38.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By patrolling, he can easily go inside the\Nresidents' houses and commit thefts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:44.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is a thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:47.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That possibility isn't entirely zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I personally don't think he would do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why else would he disguise as a police officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Arai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:10:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think that the culprit is someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I'm going to the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought he was a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:21.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Humans are hard to trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:24.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you go find that fake policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about you, Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:27.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:34.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the fake police officer is a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but this differs from what Akimoto\NYasuyo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and the others described.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:40.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:45.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm going to find some witnesses\Nrelated to the fake officer and gather more clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You also need to investigate where that person got the police uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right, that is a suspicious point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Losing a uniform should've already gotten a lot of attention...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:00.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might be hard to get a real uniform, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's a costume from a drama, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A costume from a drama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:06.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two hour drama that was broadcast last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:16.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, "The Running of 100 Police Officers."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those 100 uniforms that were used to film...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you have lost one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While we were waiting for the TV station report...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:28.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We went to find more information about\Nthe fake officer with a beard and glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The result was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:34.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That police officer appeared about a week ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently, it began last Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was the first day Yasuyo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} worked late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:47.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one saw the police officer during the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He always appears at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around the time when the last train arrives at Beika Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:53.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The times that he was seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once at the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Five times on 2nd Street...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three more times on 3rd Street...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we connect these places together...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:08.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the route Yasuyo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} takes to go home on 3rd Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:09.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the date, time, and place\Nthat the fake police officer appears...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All have connections with Akimoto Yasuyo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} working late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:20.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yasuyo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} also said it earlier, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:26.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, I saw that police officer every night that week.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:29.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing him every night, isn't this too much of a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:33.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the fake policeman intentionally appears in front of Yasuyo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:34.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what his intention is yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if we think about it that way, then\Nthe beard and glasses make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:41.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, a disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that the fake police officer\Nis someone Akimoto Yasuyo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That fake police officer is someone she knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is he then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:53.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't know? How boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Again, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I spilled it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's my handkerchief?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably dropped it at that ramen shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm scared to go there by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:07.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, let's all go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:08.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like he's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nichiuri TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:23.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:24.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:26.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He went out not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably went home to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:31.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He lives near Beika Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:32.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:38.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was one uniform they were unable to locate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:48.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:53.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That fake officer must have stolen it\Nwhile they were filming in Beika Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:53.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a Sunday, half a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:14:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was filmed on a Sunday half a month ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:05.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That'd be the third Sunday of last month, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This shop was closed on that day as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy lives near Beika Park right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably went to the filming scene during his break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If a drama's being filmed near the park, they're likely to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:24.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means he had the opportunity to lift one of the police outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the fake police officer is someone near Yasuyo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:31.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person is the fake police officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:36.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why would that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:37.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:38.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the owner chose this photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:56.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he said to use this one if we wanted to use a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:14:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This lady has a good expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:03.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy probably likes her so he chose her picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so this is her...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:13.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That owner's name is Odawara Tetsuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, he and I were high school classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the interview, both of us went drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:21.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You already have someone you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.53,0:15:24.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's a one-sided love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:25.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a scary face...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot, I already told you that you think about it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:33.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm satisfied as long as I can stay by her side watching her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:42.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't really talk much, and he looks angry all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:47.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though he seems unsocial, he's more\Ngentle and attentive than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At Tetsuryuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:55.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I talked about it with some acquaintances.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:16:00.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to work late for a whole\Nweek at the end of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:01.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a bummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't feel safe having to take the last train home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:08.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was about half a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:11.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So they heard it then, that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:13.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:18.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police officer you saw every\Nnight is definitely not a thief after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:20.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You figured it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We only have circumstantial evidence right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:26.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We still need to ask the person involved later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:30.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Upon hearing that the girl he cares about...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would be going home late for an entire week...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He started to worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.15,0:16:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If possible, he wanted to secretly guard her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:43.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was afraid that his scary face...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:47.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could cause some misunderstandings, so he gave up on the thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But not long afterward...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The case happened in this park!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:17:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He found a police uniform used in the filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:10.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He came up with an idea that would\Nallow him to guard Yasuyo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.31,0:17:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He then disguised as a police officer and appeared in front of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really dangerous for a young girl to be walking by herself at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:23.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please be extremely careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where could he have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.45,0:17:30.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:33.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that person probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:36.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Went to catch the real thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:40.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For Yasuyo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who deeply believes in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He can't do that, it's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's split up and look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:17:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With no clues, how am I supposed to catch the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that person from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though I haven't eaten yet, I smell like ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The smell on clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We met last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:50.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so drunk last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.99,0:18:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Certainly, your clothes did smell of alcohol...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.71,0:19:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, that smell was only on your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The smell was not on your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:05.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:08.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You acted that you were drunk and swayed while you walked...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:10.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you could sneak into other people's houses, didn't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:13.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.81,0:19:16.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:20.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, you thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:22.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:46.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have some questions for you about the recent serial burglaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:52.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, if you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.76,0:19:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're Odawara Tetsuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.48,0:20:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:11.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.99,0:20:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This person...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only wants to protect a young woman\Nwalking home late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to safely return her to her house,\Nhe disguised as a police officer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:36.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:42.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, mister, it is absolutely forbidden to\Ndisguise yourself as a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.35,0:20:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:49.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I trust you understand what Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.99,0:20:56.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You chose the wrong course of action.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:10.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:15.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will now place you under arrest on the charge\Nof impersonating a police officer and theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.72,0:21:16.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll continue to eat our ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.26,0:23:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.97,0:23:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the theft was his first offense...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.93,0:23:22.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And his intention in faking an identity wasn't to commit a crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.89,0:23:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, taking into account his aid in catching the thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.22,0:23:27.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was released immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We gave him strict lectures, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.10,0:23:32.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, we scolded him for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.86,0:23:35.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.28,0:23:44.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.87,0:23:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As adults, that man and woman are socially inept.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.08,0:23:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet those two wouldn't want you saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:56.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
